. Form large, broad, slightly explanate posteriorly. Antennae reaching to apical ¼ of elytra, outer segments compressed, dorsal surface of 
<number box="[810,824,446,470]" pageId="48" pageNumber="399" value="3.0">3</number>
rd without longitudinal impression found in male, 
